---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="10X Conference Coaching - Futureforth"
  description="Get the results you deserve from your next conference, summit, or trade show sponsorship."
  path="/10x"
  image="/images/10x-og.jpg"
>
  <section class="hero" id="10x">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Maximize Your Conference ROI</p>
      <h1>10X Conference Coaching</h1>
      <p class="lede" style="color:#dbe3ee;">
        The costs of sending your team to a conference, sponsoring, exhibiting, delivering demos and
        presentations, networking from your booth, and beyond add up. Sadly, conference exhibitors often
        don't see the results they had envisioned. Let's change that!
      </p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/K7DD96z1gYrfjKQM8" class="btn btn-primary">Book Your Free Session</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get Expert Coaching to Boost Your Conference and Tradeshow Success</h2>
      <p class="lede">Know what to do before, during, and after your next event.</p>

      <div class="hero__grid hero__grid--split">
        <div>
          <h3>Why Choose 10X Conference Coaching?</h3>
          <p>
            Having spent thousands of dollars to sponsor a conference, secured a booth to showcase your
            products, and earned a speaking slot to address the audience, you understand the importance
            of networking in driving your company's growth. The question now is: what are your next
            moves?
          </p>
          <p>
            With 10X Conference Coaching, you can leverage Dave's extensive experience as a Google
            speaker, published author, and seasoned exhibitor to maximize your return on investment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/nbn-book.jpg" alt="New Business Networking book cover by Dave Delaney" width="400" height="533" loading="lazy" style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); margin-inline: auto;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h3>Trusted Expertise You Can Rely On</h3>
      <p>
        As a veteran digital marketing professional and Google speaker, Dave has traveled across the US
        and Canada, delivering hundreds of presentations to thousands of people. His published book,
        &ldquo;New Business Networking,&rdquo; provides insights into effective networking at conferences
        and tradeshows online and offline. He combines storytelling, slide design, and body language to
        teach compelling presentation skills, ensuring you captivate your audience and foster valuable
        connections.
      </p>
      <h3>Tailored Strategies for Conference Success</h3>
      <p>
        From delivering impactful demonstrations and attracting booth visitors to mastering communication
        and presentation skills, Dave offers advanced strategies to enhance your conference presence.
        Whether you need creative booth ideas, content marketing expertise, or professional networking
        expertise, 10X Conference Coaching is here to help. Ask about the exclusive <em>Boots on the
        Ground</em> offer to have Dave attend, speak, and network on your behalf.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Book Your Complimentary &ldquo;Good Fit&rdquo; Coaching Session Today.</h2>
      <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">
        During your conversation, Dave will share his Three Ups of Effective Networking and how to apply
        them before your next event. Your first session is free.
      </p>
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/K7DD96z1gYrfjKQM8" class="btn btn-primary">Book Your Session</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <blockquote>&ldquo;&hellip;people love his workshop facilitation. He knows his stuff... If you have an opportunity to work together, it will be worth it.&rdquo;</blockquote>
          <cite>Speaker Manager and Lead Educator for Grow with Google</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <blockquote>&ldquo;Dave is the Real Deal! His approach and knowledge made the time and investment pay off immediately. Yes, we give Dave as many &lsquo;Thumbs Up&rsquo; as we possibly can.&rdquo;</blockquote>
          <cite>Former SVP of Culture &amp; Communications at Southwest Airlines</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <blockquote>&ldquo;&hellip;he was connecting in a very meaningful way&hellip; I wish I had learned Dave's networking insights ten years ago. He is a master communicator and storyteller, with an infectious energy that connects with audiences whether live or virtual.&rdquo;</blockquote>
          <cite>President, Nashville Technology Council</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);" class="text-center">
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/K7DD96z1gYrfjKQM8" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
